creator: IndiGG
descriptionHtml:
All gaming enthusiasts, hear us!

Introducing IndiGG Wallet, the ultimate web3 gaming wallet that lets you enter the
web3 ecosystem and earn while playing games. Players within the IndiGG DAO can now use the IndiGG Wallet to receive and redeem their earnings. They can win these earnings while playing their favourite video games by participating and winning via quests or tournaments.


Who are we?

IndiGG is India's largest web3 gaming DAO that aims to recruit 500 million gamers from the Indian subcontinent to join us in growing this exciting industry.

As a member of our DAO, you can monetize your gaming skills and earn by playing the games you love. Our platform offers a unique chance for gamers to earn without
any upfront costs.

We work closely with top gaming companies and developers around the world, to bring the best Web3 games to our DAO members. Join us and become a pioneer of the upcoming Web3 gaming industry in India.

How to earn with IndiGG?

IndiGG provides free-to-play opportunities, where players can play for free. No betting or buying of tokens or coins to play. You need to become a member, pick your favourite games, enrol in tournaments, get online and start playing one match at a time. As you play and win, you start to earn and redeem earnings. IndiGG supports games across all your favourite genres - FPS, MOBA, MMORPG, Strategy, TCG, Simulation, Sports, Fantasy and many more.

What is the IndiGG Wallet?

The IndiGG Wallet is a secure and convenient electronic wallet used by members of the IndiGG DAO to easily and safely receive earnings within the IndiGG ecosystem. Gamers on the platform will need an IndiGG wallet to manage all their transactions, including collecting their earnings.

The wallet employs Blockchain technology to record and secure every transaction. IndiGG wallet transactions ensure zero to minimum gas fees, a payment made to network verifiers for their assistance in the blockchain as a transaction fee.

-------------------------------------



IndiGG Wallet Features

1. Redeem – Once you have aggregated a certain value of earnings in your wallet, you can redeem it post the KYC process

2. Activity history – The wallet stores all your sending, receiving, and redeeming transactions in a history log for future reference.

3. Connect Social Media – You may link your Discord, Twitter, and Steam accounts to your wallet

-------------------------------------



So are you ready for the future of gaming with IndiGG? Do you have the gaming skills required to secure your earnings and gain glory?

With the IndiGG wallet, sign up to play your favourite games and play tournament matches to earn. Step into the world of Web3 Gaming as you collect earnings in your wallet.

Game on, India, with IndiGG, and start earning with the IndiGG wallet!
